@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor 买家 as Buyer
actor 卖家 as Seller
actor 管理员 as Admin
actor "运维/客服" as Support
rectangle "在线拍卖平台" as System
rectangle "第三方支付服务" as Pay
rectangle "图片或对象存储" as Storage
rectangle "邮件或短信服务" as Notify

Buyer --> System : 浏览活动/出价/支付/评价
Seller --> System : 发布物品/查看审核/确认交易/评价
Admin --> System : 审核物品/配置活动/查看报表/处理异常
Support --> System : 查看日志/协助处理纠纷

System --> Pay : 支付下单/支付查询
Pay --> System : 支付回调
System --> Storage : 上传图片/读取图片
System --> Notify : 发送邮件或短信
@enduml
